  "prompt": "What is the best website to buy customized T-shirts in India?",
  "response": "There are several websites that offer customized T-shirt services in India. Some of the most popular and highly rated ones include:\n\n1. **Vistaprint India**: Known for its high-quality prints and various customization options.\n   Website: [vistaprint.in](https://www.vistaprint.in)\n\n2. **Printvenue**: Offers a wide range of personalized products, including T-shirts.\n   Website: [printvenue.com](https://www.printvenue.com)\n\n3. **Inkmonk**: Specializes in on-demand printing for various products, including custom T-shirts.\n   Website: [inkmonk.com](https://www.inkmonk.com)\n\n4. **Alma Mater Store**: Known for customized college and school merchandise, including T-shirts.\n   Website: [almamaterstore.in](https://www.almamaterstore.in)\n\n5. **Printland**: Offers a broad selection of customizable items, including apparel.\n   Website: [printland.in](https://www.printland.in)\n\n6. **Bewakoof**: Known for trendy designs and good-quality fabrics, with options for customization.\n   Website: [bewakoof.com](https://www.bewakoof.com)\n\n7. **Fully Customized**: A platform dedicated to custom-printed apparel, including T-shirts.\n   Website: [fullycustomized.in](https://www.fullycustomized.in)\n\nThese websites provide various options for customization, such as uploading your design, choosing different styles, and selecting print types. Always consider reviews, customer service, pricing, and delivery times when choosing the best platform for your needs.",
